Subject: [PATCH 4.9 033/245] media: cpia2: fix memory leak in cpia2_usb_probe
Date:   Mon, 19 Jul 2021 16:49:35 +0200
Message-Id: <20210719144941.469909978@linuxfoundation.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.32.0
